Package: CppMatrix
Type: Package
Title: Efficient Matrix Operations using Rcpp and RcppArmadillo
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yihe Yang
Maintainer: Yihe Yang <yxy1234@case.edu>
Description: The CppMatrixFunction package provides a collection of efficient matrix operation functions implemented using Rcpp and RcppArmadillo. These functions include matrix inversion, multiplication, matrix-vector multiplication, correlation matrix computation, eigenvalue decomposition, and Kronecker product. By leveraging the power of C++ and the Armadillo library, this package offers significant performance improvements compared to base R implementations, making it suitable for computationally intensive tasks involving large matrices.
